            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut </strong>roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[325ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and add your<strong> lime leaves</strong>, <strong>fish sauce</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>coconut stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
