      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced</strong> <strong>chicken breast</strong> and<strong> ground turmeric</strong> and cook for 2-3 min</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
