            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>sliced pepper</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped ginger </strong>and <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>lemongrass inner stem</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
