    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then chop your <strong>green beans </strong>in half</p><p>Add the <strong>coconut stock</strong>, <strong>halved green beans </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 7-9 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the sauce has thickened to a curry-like consistency – this is your <strong>mild Cambodian-style chicken samla curry</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
