    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mild</strong> <strong>Cambodian-style chicken samla curry</strong> with the <strong>lemongrass rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped peanuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
